00:16:18.340 --> 00:16:21.340
Whatever you're into, it's all right with us.

00:16:21.340 --> 00:16:23.340
Just let us in on it.

00:16:23.340 --> 00:16:24.340
What's the deal?

00:16:24.340 --> 00:16:32.269
Whatever you're into, it's all right with us.

00:16:32.269 --> 00:16:35.519
Just let us in on it.

00:16:35.519 --> 00:16:36.519
What's the deal?

00:16:36.519 --> 00:16:43.860
Moses must have felt inadequate and incapable.

00:16:43.860 --> 00:16:47.860
But God has shared him that he would not be alone.

00:16:47.860 --> 00:16:50.860
I will prove to be with you, said Jehovah.

00:16:50.860 --> 00:16:56.899
Look, I don't have a boyfriend or girlfriend.

00:16:56.899 --> 00:16:58.899
I have a Bible study.

00:16:58.899 --> 00:17:00.899
I'm one of Jehovah's Witnesses.

00:17:00.899 --> 00:17:03.899
And we volunteer a time to help people learn about the Bible.

00:17:03.899 --> 00:17:04.900
The Bible?

00:17:04.900 --> 00:17:06.900
Oh, come on.

00:17:06.900 --> 00:17:07.900
That book is ancient.

00:17:07.900 --> 00:17:09.900
It closes your mind into new ideas.

00:17:09.900 --> 00:17:11.900
Actually, it doesn't.

00:17:11.900 --> 00:17:14.900
It gives people a wonderful hope for the future.

00:17:14.900 --> 00:17:17.900
Well, I believe we make our own future.

00:17:17.900 --> 00:17:20.900
I'm sorry you don't feel the same.

00:17:20.900 --> 00:17:21.900
Come on.

00:17:21.900 --> 00:17:33.279
Let's go.

00:17:33.279 --> 00:17:36.279
So, we told him I was one of Jehovah's Witnesses.

00:17:36.279 --> 00:17:38.279
I'm just glad they know now.

00:17:38.279 --> 00:17:40.279
We're so proud of you for standing up like that.

00:17:40.279 --> 00:17:42.279
Yeah, I surprised myself.

00:17:42.279 --> 00:17:45.279
I just wish it ended a little bit better.

00:17:45.279 --> 00:17:50.279
No matter the response, you made Jehovah happy today.

00:17:50.279 --> 00:17:51.279
Thanks, Grandpa.

00:17:51.279 --> 00:18:04.180
Hey.

00:18:04.180 --> 00:18:05.180
Hey.

